        },
        {
          "role": "assistant",
          "content": "### Draft Itinerary (2025\u201106\u201110 to 2025\u201106\u201114)\n\n**Day 1 \u2013 10 Jun** (Sunny, 22\u201128\u00b0C)\n- Morning: Flight FL12345 departs JFK 08:30, arrives NRT 11:45 (+1 day).\n- Afternoon: Check\u2011in at Hotel Sunroute Plaza Shinjuku (3\u2605, $130/night).\n- Evening: Visit Meiji Shrine Festival & dinner at nearby izakaya.\n\n**Day 2 \u2013 11 Jun** (Partly Cloudy)\n- Morning: Guided tour of Tsukiji Fish Market.\n- Midday: TeamLab Borderless exhibition.\n- Evening: Asakusa cultural walk and street food.\n\n**Day 3 \u2013 12 Jun** (Rainy)\n- Morning: Sushi\u2011making class (reserve ahead).\n- Afternoon: Ueno Park cherry\u2011blossom viewing.\n- Evening: Relax at hotel; optional indoor onsen.\n\n**Day 4 \u2013 13 Jun** (Sunny)\n- Full\u2011day: Day\u2011trip to Nikko (temple complex, scenic nature).\n- Evening: Return to Tokyo; Roppongi nightlife.\n\n**Day 5 \u2013 14 Jun** (Cloudy)\n- Morning: Imperial Palace garden stroll.\n- Afternoon: Last\u2011minute souvenir shopping in Shibuya.\n- Evening: Flight back on FL67890 departs NRT 17:35, arrives JFK 14:20.\n\n**Flight Options** (both within $1200 total):\n1. **FL12345** \u2013 $1150 (Delta, 1 stop in Seattle).\n2. **FL67890** \u2013 $1190 (United, 1 stop in San Francisco).\n\n**Hotel Options** (both 3\u2605, total ~ $650 for 4 nights):\n1. **Hotel Sunroute Plaza Shinjuku** \u2013 $130/night, free Wi\u2011Fi, breakfast included.\n2. **Shibuya Granbell Hotel** \u2013 $115/night, free Wi\u2011Fi, central location.\n\nThe total estimated cost (flight + hotel) is roughly $1800, leaving about $200 for activities and meals, which fits your $2000 budget.\n\nLet me know which flight and hotel you prefer, or if you\u2019d like any changes. When you\u2019re ready, I can proceed to book them for you.",
          "tool_calls": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
