        {
          "role": "assistant",
          "content": "Your travel is all set!\n\n- **Flight**: FL12345 (Delta) \u2013 booking reference **AA1B2C3D**, ticket **001234567890**.\n- **Hotel**: Hotel Sunroute Plaza Shinjuku \u2013 reservation code **HT-2025-06-10-001** for 4 nights (June\u202f10\u201114).\n\nAll payments have been processed with the stored payment method. Let me know if you need anything else such as airport transfers, restaurant reservations, or travel insurance.",
